{"tid":2497410,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"連登巴膠怒屌屎水流水線2號30分鐘一班暨衝入新界搭頭班車過海專區","createTime":"2021-04-20T13:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:51:53.000Z","uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"101853d0b4d35a25f9be75633e84eec2f8464843","tid":2497410,"uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">連登巴膠專區</span></p></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP34AZitfRXibLu1z7qScbabEaVfM2sS89WpUHEeBKWqb?filename=qn41PQX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqn41PQX.gif&h=1b2c13e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQfKaJnfUa7UwupLvXREsJwLQzsHmr2LQkjryAjsQhgZX?filename=rDiU9QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDiU9QY.jpg&h=243f0bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTc5cCLbpoeK6i26BQofn7Wezrc56WsYwLqLL2YeBRDEk?filename=vrsbsCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvrsbsCE.jpg&h=5dcb34c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPMVGzXkvecoEoxE22zoJqpP6aETDbB1EThtprP9aCCnt?filename=M1yYR4j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1yYR4j.png&h=31882cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbG7uaRzf1UEf78A5pqwa3xdkwcj1qPi6m4acYHW8AJDP?filename=xGdBDKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGdBDKk.jpg&h=af11ffec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWBW94wc6N66BB9wE63b1M5PAhL2CPJsuGU986ZAdNJ3L?filename=EM1r0XG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEM1r0XG.gif&h=a8346622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRqrJp34s4w6KhPBdvN5xLs6mZDJnP1J7ZWV4EmmSmnYi?filename=g8BPehH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8BPehH.png&h=12a266f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n連登巴膠專區三毛名單：<br />\n&bull; R730（歿）<br />\n&bull; 56185@258D - #271600<br />\n&bull; 秋本_五十鈴 - #54058<br />\n&bull; N700S - #57827</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜：Block7、無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忌：回覆、爭論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n膠talk語錄：<br />\n<br />\n1） （路線號）班客搭（其他交通選項/行路）都得啦，係佢地咁鍾情巴士。（地區名）真係好令人討厭，條條線都用幾十部車霸咁多資源，搞到其他地區唔夠車用，應該全部減一半用車量就差不多。<br />\n<br />\n2） 你屋企樓下有全日（地區名）線就唔好係度講風涼話，係度盲反 ！！！！！你唔用（路線號）唔代表其他人唔需要搭，否則為什麼區議員和居民要不斷爭取？<br />\n<br />\n3） （鐵路接駁路線號）係阻礙（地區名）巴士路線發展的絆腳石，最好取消左佢，做好對外巴士服務。<br />\n<br />\n4） （起點）可以去（上車站位）搭（路線號），步行也不算太遠！<br />\n<br />\n5） （持份者）對（地區名）存有歧視及欺凌態度，鐵證如山，甚至早在（時間點）前已經出現，咩野（上述地區人士之戲稱）論，不攻自破。唔認同唔緊要，歡迎拎數據拎道理黎插到我口啞啞。拎唔到既，可以唔出聲唔使理我。又要出聲，又剩係識含血噴人人身攻擊，咁叫高質素既討論？除左含血噴人人身攻擊同留低個負皮，還有甚麼板釜？<br />\n<br />\n6） 呢度部分人只係識盲反（路線號），盲反（地區名）巴士線，非理性討論，毫無建樹，一啲出色都無。唔高興，意見不合就只係發惡話飛走（地區名），毫無建設性。<br />\n<br />\n7） 總之任何反對改善（地區名）巴士服務的人，就要被聲討。<br />\n<br />\n8） 其他人要求改善其他地區服務就得，我地提出改善（地區名）巴士服務就講乜都唔合心意，根本就係盲反。<br />\n<br />\n9） （地區名）點解可以做到大帝，獨攬（全/各）區所有（路線種類）線？<br />\n<br />\n10） （地區1）成為改線絆腳石囉，有條（路線A）都要死攬（路線B），呢啲咪真大帝囉。整個（地區2）對（路線B）既期望就係改快，改都唔改就取消，會唔會過份左啲呢？因為（地區名）反對，就要推倒，而（巴士公司）又要咁聽話，我真係唔知係乜野道理。<br />\n<br />\n11) 當個世界係圍住 (地區) 轉當正自己係地球中心的野，無野值得睇，但班人批鬥 (區議員) 就有問題。<br />\n<br />\n12）住(某地區）二線地區唔係仲諗住有跨區線呀？ 自己出（某地區）市中心轉啦"},{"pid":"9b785b349324e6b32365423e76ab1ac27202430e","tid":2497410,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢標題嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連屎水東區過海四線同厹白石角過海開線都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407990d93cf0c380fff3ad474c075dfc4813e993","tid":2497410,"uid":218731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"上到青沙等900但佢頂閘點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77b63668f8a5a1ed789f35524b46d0e9fc35bee","tid":2497410,"uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b785b349324e6b32365423e76ab1ac27202430e","tid":2497410,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢標題嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連屎水東區過海四線同厹白石角過海開線都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"衝入新界咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d494258027c914d177c6ba12756c25ad82657e","tid":2497410,"uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"407990d93cf0c380fff3ad474c075dfc4813e993","tid":2497410,"uid":218731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"上到青沙等900但佢頂閘點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"厹：請善用280X轉乘優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f52125e5d09ade7bc8b376cfb804650d9ae93d","tid":2497410,"uid":117979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"衝去塔厹公四蚊港島流水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e289a2c512e5bc153f9069f679eee468b1fd3533","tid":2497410,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b77b63668f8a5a1ed789f35524b46d0e9fc35bee","tid":2497410,"uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b785b349324e6b32365423e76ab1ac27202430e","tid":249