src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd5EWdxb2vZuSypUCcTbAg3BfAyKiJY37CvpgUMGgDD7y?filename=ZmNz19y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmNz19y.png&h=e7a36c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSaui9k161Yrr9CmQbV4DvUpQzDbjbrxdgRnEJ9n3u3wX?filename=QV74EWj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV74EWj.png&h=ecc1c5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好地地出條片咪算囉<br />\n又要遮遮掩掩<br />\n但係又遮d唔遮d遮唔晒<br />\n結果大家就係咁搵錯處<br />\n搞錯晒出片嘅原意</blockquote>其實係咪厹派咗商業間諜入屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遮住就係為咗提醒有每程只需9.8呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n欲蓋彌彰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n厹不費一兵一卒就收到月票宣傳功效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw cap多張<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUncDgd4vWB3PPPmvABrTkkBhskg1JMtxc8g5sNA8xZjq?filename=NwwQAJx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwwQAJx.png&h=c91561d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4569719f0c163384c9bb9663c87bec5c2def423c","tid":2497410,"uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"701aa318e4a2d04c089f60d4d66f9a63cd60edab","tid":2497410,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"厹係咪咁驚唔夠客<br />\n900開10個分段想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"擺明想同屎水隻揪"},{"pid":"612f69cf6503e7c9a1c9e7aa9bbfefc52cba1470","tid":2497410,"uid":200210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4569719f0c163384c9bb9663c87bec5c2def423c","tid":2497410,"uid":310005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"701aa318e4a2d04c089f60d4d66f9a63cd60edab","tid":24974